                            <comment id="12852596" author="pkamath" created="Thu, 1 Apr 2010 23:21:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The earlier patch was using System.getProperty(&quot;java.home&quot;) - apparently ant sometimes appends &quot;jre&quot; to $JAVA_HOME as the value of the java.home property - this causes failures since $JAVA_HOME/jre/bin/ does not contain javac. I have changed this code to use System.getEnv(&quot;JAVA_HOME&quot;) instead.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
